Author: Duskyroses
Text: I think I ate just about the same before but maybe I subconsciously am eating higher volume. Now that you mention it I’m eating a lot of Shiritaki Noodles whereas I wasn’t before...

Author: yyyyy622
Text: Could it also be because you changed what you eat? I tend to eat less processed foods when restricting just so I can eat larger quantities. And sometimes junk food can trigger me so cutting it out helps me in that sense .
